data.description: Welcome Home!  This tri-level is located on a spacious double size .35 acre lot and is move-in ready, featuring gleaming hardwoods, vaulted ceilings, and recess lighting throughout.   The home has  4 BR and 2 Full BA,  a electric fireplace for cozy warm gatherings with friends and family, and plenty of natural light streaming through.       Upstairs are 3 bedrooms with a gorgeous remodeled Bath and frameless shower, smart mirror, chrome fixtures plus more.     The kitchen has been updated with gorgeous marbled grey granite countertops, ceramic tile flooring, new cabinetry, and SS barn sink/fixtures.   The dining area is just off the kitchen and leads out to a 10X10 deck that overlooks a large yard for entertaining and outdoor living.  The 4th Bedroom and Laundry room are located on the lower level.    The second bath on the lower level has also been remodeled with a Smart/tech mirror/Bluetooth speakers, CAT5 Wiring, and a Smart Thermostat.    Two sump pumps have been installed in the basement and have a lifetime warranty.   The Recreation room has new gray LVP flooring and leads to the walkout basement.  The roof is less than three years old.   HVAC/Heat Pump and Hot Water Heater-2020.   Large storage shed in the back for your man cave or use for projects/crafting.  There is an additional storage shed, as-is below the deck for extra storage and there is extra storage under the staircase.   Offering also the possibility of a lower rate as this is a VA Assumable!  The home sits at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac and is close to  I95, Rt 3, Shopping, restaurants plus more.   Don't let this one get away!
